And he had been offered a job over here at Texas A&M 
University to head the planning program because

17:07.049 --> 17:16.363
they had, actually, when he was here in 
architecture, they had proposed a planning

17:07.049 --> 17:16.363
program, and it was not approved. But it had 
finally gotten approved around the middle 60s.

17:19.413 --> 17:21.477
And so he was asked if he would come and have that 
program. So he had done that in, I believe it was in

