19:16.440 --> 19:24.171
top-notch people looking over my shoulder, like 
Francis from Berkeley, who was a special

19:16.440 --> 19:24.171
consultant. He was down there. Well, he was at 
Berkeley, but he went down there once during the

19:25.133 --> 19:30.180
process, or twice. But he had been in Latin America 
for many years before that, so he knew the country

19:30.700 --> 19:34.865
well and a lot of the people there. And he was a 
recognized international consultant in Latin

19:35.605 --> 19:41.151
America, and actually elsewhere, too, in Europe. 
